{
  "page": "Sylva Santagar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Santagar\" title=\"House Santagar\"><img alt=\"House Santagar.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/98/House_Santagar.svg/50px-House_Santagar.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/98/House_Santagar.svg/75px-House_Santagar.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/98/House_Santagar.svg/100px-House_Santagar.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Sylva Santagar</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Estermont\" title=\"House Estermont\"><img alt=\"House Estermont.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/50px-House_Estermont.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/75px-House_Estermont.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/100px-House_Estermont.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Sylva_Santagar_by_Rae_Lavergne.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sylva Santagar by Rae Lavergne.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Sylva_Santagar_by_Rae_Lavergne.jpg/350px-Sylva_Santagar_by_Rae_Lavergne.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Sylva_Santagar_by_Rae_Lavergne.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Sylva Santagar, by Rae Lavergne ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nSpotted Sylva</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Greenstone\" title=\"Greenstone\">Greenstone</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Santagar\" title=\"House Santagar\">House Santagar</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Estermont\" title=\"House Estermont\">House Estermont</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_276_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">276&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_277_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">277&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Spottswood\" title=\"Spottswood\">Spottswood</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsylva_santagar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsylva_santagar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Santagar\" title=\"Symon Santagar\">Symon Santagar</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Eldon_Estermont\" title=\"Eldon Estermont\">Eldon Estermont</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sylva Santagar</b>, known as <b>Spotted Sylva</b>, is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Santagar\" title=\"House Santagar\">House Santagar</a>. She is the heir of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Santagar\" title=\"Symon Santagar\">Symon Santagar</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Spottswood\" title=\"Knight of Spottswood\">Knight of Spottswood</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Sylva\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Sylva</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Sylva\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Sylva</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Sylva_Santagar\" title=\"Category:Images of Sylva Santagar\">Images of Sylva Santagar</a></div>\n<p>Sylva has many freckles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Sylva is a childhood friend of Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> They were children at the <a href=\"/index.php/Water_Gardens\" title=\"Water Gardens\">Water Gardens</a> together, usually a group of five, along with <a href=\"/index.php/Tyene_Sand\" title=\"Tyene Sand\">Tyene Sand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Garin\" title=\"Garin\">Garin</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Andrey_Dalt\" title=\"Andrey Dalt\">Andrey Dalt</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Because of her freckles, Sylva received the nickname \"Spotted Sylva\". Her friends like to pretend the nickname comes from the fact that she is the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/Spottswood\" title=\"Spottswood\">Spottswood</a>, as the Santagars' sigil is a spotted <a href=\"/index.php/Leopard\" title=\"Leopard\">leopard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/63/Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg/350px-Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"356\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/63/Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg/525px-Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/63/Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg/700px-Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sylva_Santagar_by_Lopata_Four.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sylva by Lopata Four</div></div></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> invites Sylva to be one her co-conspirators to make Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_the_Andals,_the_Rhoynar,_and_the_First_Men\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men\">Queen of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men</a>. During their travels, they are intercepted by <a href=\"/index.php/Areo_Hotah\" title=\"Areo Hotah\">Areo Hotah</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a>. Sylva is among those captured.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Though <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a>, deigns not to punish Sylva for her role in the conspiracy, she is sent home to her father, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Santagar\" title=\"Symon Santagar\">Symon Santagar</a>. Symon quickly <a href=\"/index.php/Betrothal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Betrothal\">betroths</a> Sylva to the aged <a href=\"/index.php/Eldon_Estermont\" title=\"Eldon Estermont\">Eldon Estermont</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Greenstone\" title=\"Lord of Greenstone\">Lord of Greenstone</a>. Sylva is sent to <a href=\"/index.php/Greenstone\" title=\"Greenstone\">Greenstone</a> and married soon after.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Sylva\">Quotes by Sylva</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Sylva\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Arianne</b>: Might I present Lady Sylva Santagar, my queen? My dearest Spotted Sylva.<br />\n</p><p><b>Myrcella</b>: Why do they call you that?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Sylva</b>: For my freckles, Your Grace, though they all pretend it is because I am the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/Spottswood\" title=\"Spottswood\">Spottswood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a>, and Sylva</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Sylva\">Quotes about Sylva</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Sylva\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Andrey_Dalt\" title=\"Andrey Dalt\">Drey</a> and Spotted Sylva were her dearest friends, aside from her cousin <a href=\"/index.php/Tyene_Sand\" title=\"Tyene Sand\">Tyene</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_(orphan)\" title=\"Garin (orphan)\">Garin</a> had been teasing her since both of them were drinking from his mother's teats, but just now she was in no mood for japery.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Lady Sylva received no punishment from me, but she was of an age to marry. <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Santagar\" title=\"Symon Santagar\">Her father</a> has shipped her to <a href=\"/index.php/Greenstone\" title=\"Greenstone\">Greenstone</a> to wed <a href=\"/index.php/Elden_Estermont\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Elden Estermont\">Lord Estermont</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylva_Santagar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px soli